or I wouldn't be in here.

23
00:03:39.636 --> 00:03:40.846
I'm sorry. Sam.

24
00:03:42.181 --> 00:03:45.200
You're gonna say this to me
after all we've been through?

25
00:03:45.225 --> 00:03:46.827
Want me to wait till Sandy gets in?

26
00:03:46.852 --> 00:03:49.563
I don't want you to say it.

27
00:03:51.607 --> 00:03:54.835
Please. Sheriff. Don't say it.

28
00:03:54.860 --> 00:03:56.295
- Deputy Marnes...
- Please. Sheriff.

29
00:03:56.320 --> 00:03:57.529
I wanna go out.

30
00:04:08.916 --> 00:04:11.335
While you get things rolling.
I think I'm gonna lie down.

31
00:06:17.878 --> 00:06:19.104
Are you getting coffee?

32
00:06:19.129 --> 00:06:20.355
I am!

33
00:06:20.380 --> 00:06:24.009
Okay. I'll take milk. please.
Actually. no milk. I don't...

34
00:06:24.510 --> 00:06:26.278
I don't need any milk. No.

35
00:06:26.303 --> 00:06:28.180
- Come on. It's almost 8:00.
- Okay.

36
00:06:28.722 --> 00:06:30.182
- Please.
- Okay. coming.

37
00:06:32.476 --> 00:06:33.477
Thanks.

38
00:06:35.062 --> 00:06:36.121
I don't know why we're doing this.

39
00:06:36.146 --> 00:06:38.607
We're not gonna get it.
We had two tries.

40
00:06:52.621 --> 00:06:54.039
I can't believe it.

41
00:06:54.623 --> 00:06:55.641
Third time's a charm.

42
00:06:55.666 --> 00:06:57.684
You're just excited to have sex every day.

43
00:06:57.709 --> 00:06:59.520
Hey. you could be pregnant
a month from now.

44
00:06:59.545 --> 00:07:01.171
Please let it be more than that.

45
00:07:06.134 --> 00:07:07.719
You know I love you no matter what.

46
00:07:08.554 --> 00:07:10.931
Shut up. We're doing this. Let's go.

47
00:07:11.682 --> 00:07:14.076
Allie.
his office doesn't open for an hour.

48
00:07:14.101 --> 00:07:15.828
Yeah. Well. we can get some breakfast.

49
00:07:15.853 --> 00:07:17.412
We can talk about baby names.

50
00:07:17.437 --> 00:07:20.165
Which will be me just humoring you.
because obviously.

51
00:07:20.190 --> 00:07:22.209
if I'm giving birth
to this little critter.

52
00:07:22.234 --> 00:07:24.194
I'm naming it whatever the hell I want.

53
00:07:26.071 --> 00:07:27.072
Okay.

54
00:07:37.749 --> 00:07:39.585
- Good luck.
- Thanks.

55
00:07:40.335 --> 00:07:42.146
- Congratulations.
- Yeah. Thank you.

56
00:07:42.171 --> 00:07:43.255
Thanks.

57
00:07:46.008 --> 00:07:46.925
Hi.

58
00:07:47.426 --> 00:07:48.343
Hi. Congrats.

59
00:07:49.970 --> 00:07:51.013
Hi.

60
00:07:54.725 --> 00:07:56.577
I really hate this part.

61
00:07:56.602 --> 00:07:58.245
People are just happy for us.

62
00:07:58.270 --> 00:08:00.856
I just wish everyone didn't know.

63
00:08:03.025 --> 00:08:04.001
Oh. shit.

64
00:08:04.026 --> 00:08:06.211
