- Clever.

79
00:08:37.643 --> 00:08:40.729
I have no desire to be sent out.
Thank you. Sheriff.

80
00:08:41.855 --> 00:08:45.859
Mrs. Becker. if you have an open mind.
come see me.

81
00:08:47.611 --> 00:08:49.071
