108
00:10:27.794 --> 00:10:28.770
Remember last time?

109
00:10:28.795 --> 00:10:31.356
At some point.
this is gonna start feeling like work.

110
00:10:31.381 --> 00:10:32.591
Best work ever.

111
00:10:41.558 --> 00:10:44.453
We tried. like. four times
before we finally got clearance.

112
00:10:44.478 --> 00:10:45.746
so now's your time.

113
00:10:45.771 --> 00:10:46.855
Yeah. let's hope.

114
00:10:47.481 --> 00:10:48.582
{\an8}My cousin Charlene.

115
00:10:48.607 --> 00:10:52.085
{\an8}she convinced her husband
he had to dye his unit blue.

116
00:10:52.110 --> 00:10:53.170
{\an8}Did it work?

117
00:10:53.195 --> 00:10:54.379
{\an8}They got pregnant.

118
00:10:54.404 --> 00:10:57.508
{\an8}But I'm sure his blue dick
had nothing to do with it.

119
00:10:57.533 --> 00:11:00.469
She was just fucking with him.
Gives you a clue to that marriage.

120
00:11:00.494 --> 00:11:02.763
- Hello. Bernard.
- Morning. Bernard.

121
00:11:02.788 --> 00:11:04.498
Karen. Allison.

122
00:11:05.624 --> 00:11:07.559
I see you posted an article

123
00:11:07.584 --> 00:11:10.771
